OL,3,CCouncil forced to apologise as rubbish
OL,4,Cdumped by roads
OL,6,FNottingham City Council has issued a
OL,7,F"sincere apology" after workers were
OL,8,Fcaught dumping rubbish by a busy road.
OL,10,FThe pictures, taken from a property
OL,11,Fnear Western Boulevard, show multiple
OL,12,Fcouncil workers picking up litter with
OL,13,Fshovels and rakes and dumping it onto
OL,14,Fthe grassy knoll on Newland Close.
OL,16,FThe workers, who had been tasked with
OL,17,Fcleaning up the area, were spotted by
OL,18,Fa resident who lives nearby on
OL,19,FThursday 20 February.
