OL,6,FThe rubbish then reportedly made its
OL,7,Fway onto Newland Close itself and into
OL,8,Fthe residents' gardens on the road.
OL,10,FThe issue came to light after a
OL,11,Fcouncil-run Facebook page, "My
OL,12,FNottingham", posted a warning to those
OL,13,Ffly-tipping across Nottingham.
OL,15,FIn response to this, the resident
OL,16,Fasked them to explain the pictures.
