OL,3,CCouncil forced to apologise as rubbish
OL,4,Cdumped by roads
OL,6,FNottingham City Council sent out a
OL,7,Fteam to clean up the mess that the
OL,8,Fprevious council workers had made
OL,9,Fafter it was reported that they were
OL,10,Fseen littering while at work.
OL,12,FA council spokesperson said: "We
OL,13,Fsincerely apologise for this incident
OL,14,Fand acknowledge that this is not
OL,15,Fstandard practice.
OL,17,FAs soon as the matter was brought to
OL,18,Four attention, the team was
OL,19,Fimmediately sent back the same day to
OL,20,Fclear the rubbish and ensure the area
OL,21,Fwas left in a clean and tidy state.
