OL,6,F"We take these concerns seriously and
OL,7,Fare reinforcing the correct procedures
OL,8,Fwith our teams to prevent any
OL,9,Frecurrence.
OL,11,F"Our commitment remains to maintaining
OL,12,Fhigh standards of cleanliness and
OL,13,Fenvironmental responsibility across
OL,14,Fthe city."
